 <div class="container">
   <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
     <div class="text-center">
       <h1 class="display-1"> One service today!</h1>
         <h3>  Worship with us at 9 a.m. Or participate from home using our Live stream to YouTube, <%= link_to "Click here", "#{@worship.url}" %></h3>
         <h3>There is a special presentation in Trinity Hall after the mass, all about putting your affairs in order. This is a great gift for those you leave behind...</h3>

     </div>
 </div>
